trans-unit.source: . In Riak, the buckets are replicated, to avoid data loss, and instead of a router, they use consistent hashing to map a bucket to a node. A consistent hashing algorithm helps reduce the amount of data that needs to be migrated when new storage nodes are added to your live system.
trans-unit.target: 。在Riak中，存储桶被复制以避免数据丢失，并且它们使用一致的散列而不是路由器来将存储桶映射到节点。当将新的存储节点添加到实时系统中时，一致的哈希算法有助于减少需要迁移的数据量。

trans-unit.source: . Processes usually run under supervision trees which are themselves processes that listen to exit signals from the supervised processes. Once an exit signal is received, the supervision strategy kicks in and the supervised process is restarted.
trans-unit.target: 。流程通常在监督树下运行，监督树本身就是侦听受监督流程的 exit 信号的流程。一旦收到 exit 信号，监管策略就会启动，并且受监管的流程会重新启动。
